              "type": "string",
              "value": "=A compact, formidable futuristic cyberpunk factory, 3D casual game asset. The building showcases an asymmetrical, brutalist-inspired, multi-tiered design with sharp angles and imposing slopes, primarily in deep black and stark white. Explosive, contrasting blood-red and electric yellow glowing panels are strategically placed on the facades, along with razor-sharp cyan linear light accents outlining key structural divisions. Harsh, focused light spills from wide, horizontal vents, and intermittent, blinding flashes of lime green light emanate from integrated power conduits. Above the main entrance, a small, semi-transparent, holographic gear icon shimmers with a vibrant, almost violent, magenta glow. A large, volumetric and semi-transparent neon blue hologram of a hard hat is positioned above the central, tallest section of the factory, its form subtly shifting with a cold, digital hum. Clean, readable design, no clutter. Isometric view, soft glowing lighting, isolated on a light, solid background. CGI render, casual game style."
